graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[Controller Manager]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Metrics[Metrics Endpoint<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
    end

    subgraph "Model Registry Instance"
        RestAPI[REST API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        gRPCAPI[gRPC API<br/>9090/TCP]

        OAuthProxy -->|proxies to| RestAPI
        RBACProxy -->|proxies to| RestAPI
    end

    subgraph "Storage Layer"
        PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP)]
        MySQL[(MySQL<br/>3306/TCP)]
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>v1beta1]
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Model Registry Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| Services[Kubernetes Services]
    Controller -->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    Controller -->|creates| RBAC[RBAC Resources]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[Network Policies]
    Controller -->|optionally creates| PostgreSQL

    Deployment -->|runs| RestAPI
    Deployment -->|runs| OAuthProxy
    Deployment -->|runs| RBACProxy
    Deployment -->|runs| gRPCAPI

    RestAPI -->|connects to| PostgreSQL
    RestAPI -->|connects to| MySQL

    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Controller -->|depends on| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>optional]
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server]

    Controller -->|integrates with| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>optional]
    Istio -->|auth via| Authorino[Authorino<br/>optional]

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| Metrics

